channel.title: Lagging out
channel.description: Hey guys I added a custom item to my server, but every time I spawn it, it laggs me out and it won't let me log on unless I go to my character file and get rid of the custom, any help?

item.title: Lagging out
item.dc:creator: @purestmage74 purestmage74
item.description:
@purestmage74 wrote:

Most likely messed up on the models ID’s Client sided.
Know that happens with some npcs spawned if you don’t have their models, but you let your server attempt to display them, if you put your cursor over something that isn’t being displayed it will cause lagg.
